ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/M%C3%A3-Ng%C3%B4i-pha/poem-DXnb42iAf81brgJQgbWaDw">Mã Ngôi pha - 馬嵬坡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-C%C6%A1/Mai-Pha/poem-zD5VHROF90R0_LK8mkq5LA">Mai Pha - 梅坡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-C%C6%A1/author-Onk53GrYSBQGT7xscWqNaw">Từ Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/M%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-II-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-FhWFRMckMTH01zJADnVoWg">Mạn hứng (II) kỳ 1 - 漫興其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Li%E1%BB%85n/T%E1%BB%91ng-Thi%C3%AAm-hi%E1%BA%BFn-V%C5%A9-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3n-ph%C3%B3-Giao-Ch%E1%BB%89-tham-t%C3%A1n-Anh-qu%E1%BB%91c-c%C3%B4ng/poem-hN164gjmOTJWtbaPAFTMXQ">Tống Thiêm hiến Vũ Đại Bản phó Giao Chỉ tham tán Anh quốc công - 送僉憲武大本赴交阯參贊英國公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Li%E1%BB%85n/author-HAbvYJCXYNaPegkfHwS9XQ">Trần Liễn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/V%C5%A9-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%B9ng-Phong-c%C3%A1c/poem--RZ9Jn4HmCKliMa4SEQc0g">Vũ Xương Tùng Phong các - 武昌松風閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
